07:23:17.279 --> 07:23:17.819
tribes.

07:23:17.880 --> 07:23:20.040
So we wanted to give you some basic

07:23:20.040 --> 07:23:22.259
information that may be useful as you get

07:23:22.259 --> 07:23:22.919
to know one another.

07:23:22.979 --> 07:23:26.040
