07:23:32.639 --> 07:23:35.580
You are the hope of Pyre's future.

07:23:35.639 --> 07:23:38.639
You are the dragons who can bring lasting

07:23:38.639 --> 07:23:39.419
peace to this world.

07:23:39.479 --> 07:23:43.020
We wish you all the power of wings of

07:23:43.020 --> 07:23:43.200
fire.

